data.description: Less than 2 year old home + SALTWATER POOL in Beautiful & Desirable Wells Creek! Convenient location w/quick access to I-95 & I-295, shopping,  restaurants, Jacksonville & St. Augustine. Nature filled drive into the neighborhood w/walking paths & community amenities including an amazingly nice dog park & so much more. Pool has low maintenance, durable travertine decking for slip & heat resistance! 3 deck jets & changing color LED lighting. Pool is also pre-wired for a heater. Relax & enjoy it all from your covered Lanai w/ceiling fan. Inside features an open floor plan w/ceramic tile flooring. Kitchen w/quartz countertops, gas stove & walk-in pantry. Primary BR is spacious & bright + attached bath w/quartz countertops & walk-in closet w/custom built-ins. Appraisal from February 2023 available. Bring your best offer!
